title: Ubehage's EasyCopy v2.4
description:
Ubehage's EasyCopy v2.4
-----------------------
"Small, Fast and Easy to use!"

Here is a new release of this user- and nerd-friendly tool for copying/moving around with files and folders.

I have a added a small file-browser for your convenience. In some aspects, it can be easier and faster to use than Windows Explorer.


Updates in this release:
- New File-browser. Accessible via the Main menu, or by pressing CTRL+F4.
- Some of the system-code has been rewritten and optimized.
